This is the README file for Term::UI.

Please refer to 'perldoc Term::UI' after installation for details.

#####################################################################

* Description

Term::UI provides methods to ask both elaborate questions as well
as simple yes/no questions via a Term::ReadLine interface using a
template. It can also parse options per unix style.

#####################################################################

* Installation

Term::UI follows the standard perl module install process

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

The module uses no C or XS parts, so no c-compiler is required.

